  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Nalbuphine as an adjuvant to bupivacaine caudal anesthesia for postoperative analgesia in
      children undergoing inguinal hernia repair.

      2 groups, 30 patients each
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
